    "student_name": "熊子妍",
    "assigned_section": "13点；18点；次日2点",
    "word_task_type": "pragmatic_meaning",
    "sentence_task_type": "free_translation"
  },
  "source_text": {
    "text_id": "text_001",
    "title": "《地书》白话版选段",
    "source": "教师提供",
    "raw_text": "===13点===\n我走在斑马线上，心里盘算着给她准备一份生日礼物——她马上就要30岁了。\n我又想到，要是送她一份求婚礼物，我们就能结婚了，可送什么好呢？\n她喜欢香奈儿，可我没钱，买不起。\n走着走着，我看到一家书店，想到书也是个不错的礼物。\n我走进书店，翻了翻书，突然想到可以在书里夹一朵玫瑰，可玫瑰很快就枯萎了，我的心也跟着碎了。我又想到书里藏着坏人，用枪指着我，有点害怕。\n\n坏人开枪打我，我躲开了，有点生气。我看着机票，想去旅行，忍不住笑了。\n我想到我们结婚后去度蜜月，笑了。我拿起手机给她发消息。\n我问她：“结婚后想去哪度蜜月？”她回：“想去自由女神像，还有埃菲尔铁塔……”\n电话响了，我看着机票，想去悉尼歌剧院、富士山、泰姬陵、加拿大、金字塔……最后选了美国。\n美国的景点有白宫、迪士尼、梦露、体育馆、自由女神像、世贸中心。\n我想到世贸中心被炸了，有点惊讶。\n我查了去美国的航班、机场、酒店和攻略。\n各种酒店都列了出来，五星的、三星的、经济型的，还有博物馆、剧院，各种奢侈品品牌。\n我点了赞，笑着继续翻书，走着走着到了门口，红灯亮了，停了下来。\n我想到她，转身往回走，又查了巴黎的景点，巴黎圣母院、蒙娜丽莎、埃菲尔铁塔……到了门口。\n\n我刷卡结账，想着买两本书当礼物。\n付了钱，拿到了礼物，想到她会很开心。\n我看着礼物，纠结要不要送她。\n走出书店，想到她的生日，又回头看了看。\n我想着相机太贵，不买；平板太贵，不买；滑板太贵，不买；游戏不贵，买了，忍不住笑了。\n\n我想到她和游戏，还是去结账吧。\n结完账，走出书店，看了看时间，回公司。\n刷了工牌，走进电梯，看到快递的牌子，有点惊讶。\n按了电梯，电梯到了1、2……89楼，红灯停了，开门，出去。\n左转，直行，转弯，直行，再转弯，直行，打卡，刷手机，开门。\n走到工位，坐下。\n\n===18点===\n下午六点，我回到家，第一件事就是打开空调，让自己凉快下来。我从冰箱里拿出饮料，惬意地喝了一口。然后，我走进浴室冲了个澡，出来后开始精心挑选晚上约会要穿的衣服，试了好几套，终于找到了满意的搭配。我吹了吹头发，听着音乐，心情格外舒畅。\n与此同时，她也在家忙碌着。她戴上眼镜和帽子，仔细地挑选口红颜色，涂好口红后，又认真地化了妆，吹了头发。她也在听着音乐，准备出门。\n我选好了鞋子和配饰，准备出门。出门前，我给她发了条消息，确认了时间。然后关掉空调和手机，离开了家。刚出门不久，她的电话就打了过来，我有点紧张地接了电话。挂了电话后，我直奔花店，买了 12 朵漂亮的花。\n我拿着花，心里想着她，想象着她收到花时开心的样子。终于，我见到了她，把花递给了她。她开心地接过花，我们相视而笑。\n我们一起去了约定的酒吧。在酒吧里，她问我要不要回家，但我更想和她在这里多待一会儿。我们点了啤酒，聊着天。突然，我看到一些奇怪的东西，感到有些惊讶。不过，和她在一起的时光总是很愉快，虽然中途我去了趟洗手间，但这并不影响我们的好心情。\n\n===次日2点===\n凌晨两点，我躺在床上，很快就进入了梦乡。在梦里，我看到两个人在激烈地争吵。接着，我梦见了 2012 年世界末日的场景，巨大的海浪淹没了地球，人们纷纷逃到山上避难。",
    "notes": "包含13点、18点、次日2点三个章节"
  },
  "units": [
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_001",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我走在斑马线上，心里盘算着给她准备一份生日礼物——她马上就要30岁了。",
      "sentence_index": 1,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 35
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_002",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我又想到，要是送她一份求婚礼物，我们就能结婚了，可送什么好呢？",
      "sentence_index": 2,
      "char_start": 35,
      "char_end": 66
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_003",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "她喜欢香奈儿，可我没钱，买不起。",
      "sentence_index": 3,
      "char_start": 66,
      "char_end": 82
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_004",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "走着走着，我看到一家书店，想到书也是个不错的礼物。",
      "sentence_index": 4,
      "char_start": 82,
      "char_end": 107
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_005",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我走进书店，翻了翻书，突然想到可以在书里夹一朵玫瑰，可玫瑰很快就枯萎了，我的心也跟着碎了。",
      "sentence_index": 5,
      "char_start": 107,
      "char_end": 152
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_006",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我又想到书里藏着坏人，用枪指着我，有点害怕。",
      "sentence_index": 6,
      "char_start": 152,
      "char_end": 174
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_007",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "坏人开枪打我，我躲开了，有点生气。",
      "sentence_index": 7,
      "char_start": 174,
      "char_end": 191
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_008",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我看着机票，想去旅行，忍不住笑了。",
      "sentence_index": 8,
      "char_start": 191,
      "char_end": 208
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_009",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我想到我们结婚后去度蜜月，笑了。",
      "sentence_index": 9,
      "char_start": 208,
      "char_end": 224
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_010",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我拿起手机给她发消息。",
      "sentence_index": 10,
      "char_start": 224,
      "char_end": 235
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_011",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我问她：“结婚后想去哪度蜜月？”",
      "sentence_index": 11,
      "char_start": 235,
      "char_end": 252
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_012",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "”她回：“想去自由女神像，还有埃菲尔铁塔……”电话响了，我看着机票，想去悉尼歌剧院、富士山、泰姬陵、加拿大、金字塔……最后选了美国。",
      "sentence_index": 12,
      "char_start": 251,
      "char_end": 317
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_013",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "美国的景点有白宫、迪士尼、梦露、体育馆、自由女神像、世贸中心。",
      "sentence_index": 13,
      "char_start": 316,
      "char_end": 348
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_014",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我想到世贸中心被炸了，有点惊讶。",
      "sentence_index": 14,
      "char_start": 348,
      "char_end": 364
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_015",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我查了去美国的航班、机场、酒店和攻略。",
      "sentence_index": 15,
      "char_start": 364,
      "char_end": 383
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_016",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "各种酒店都列了出来，五星的、三星的、经济型的，还有博物馆、剧院，各种奢侈品品牌。",
      "sentence_index": 16,
      "char_start": 383,
      "char_end": 423
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_017",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我点了赞，笑着继续翻书，走着走着到了门口，红灯亮了，停了下来。",
      "sentence_index": 17,
      "char_start": 423,
      "char_end": 454
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_018",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我想到她，转身往回走，又查了巴黎的景点，巴黎圣母院、蒙娜丽莎、埃菲尔铁塔……到了门口。",
      "sentence_index": 18,
      "char_start": 454,
      "char_end": 497
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_019",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我刷卡结账，想着买两本书当礼物。",
      "sentence_index": 19,
      "char_start": 497,
      "char_end": 513
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_020",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "付了钱，拿到了礼物，想到她会很开心。",
      "sentence_index": 20,
      "char_start": 513,
      "char_end": 531
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_021",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我看着礼物，纠结要不要送她。",
      "sentence_index": 21,
      "char_start": 531,
      "char_end": 545
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_022",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "走出书店，想到她的生日，又回头看了看。",
      "sentence_index": 22,
      "char_start": 545,
      "char_end": 564
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_023",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我想着相机太贵，不买；平板太贵，不买；滑板太贵，不买；游戏不贵，买了，忍不住笑了。",
      "sentence_index": 23,
      "char_start": 564,
      "char_end": 605
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_024",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我想到她和游戏，还是去结账吧。",
      "sentence_index": 24,
      "char_start": 605,
      "char_end": 620
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_025",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "结完账，走出书店，看了看时间，回公司。",
      "sentence_index": 25,
      "char_start": 620,
      "char_end": 639
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_026",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "刷了工牌，走进电梯，看到快递的牌子，有点惊讶。",
      "sentence_index": 26,
      "char_start": 639,
      "char_end": 662
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_027",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "按了电梯，电梯到了1、2……89楼，红灯停了，开门，出去。",
      "sentence_index": 27,
      "char_start": 662,
      "char_end": 691
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_028",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "左转，直行，转弯，直行，再转弯，直行，打卡，刷手机，开门。",
      "sentence_index": 28,
      "char_start": 691,
      "char_end": 720
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_029",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "走到工位，坐下。",
      "sentence_index": 29,
      "char_start": 720,
      "char_end": 728
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_030",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "下午六点，我回到家，第一件事就是打开空调，让自己凉快下来。",
      "sentence_index": 30,
      "char_start": 728,
      "char_end": 757
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_031",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我从冰箱里拿出饮料，惬意地喝了一口。",
      "sentence_index": 31,
      "char_start": 757,
      "char_end": 775
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_032",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "然后，我走进浴室冲了个澡，出来后开始精心挑选晚上约会要穿的衣服，试了好几套，终于找到了满意的搭配。",
      "sentence_index": 32,
      "char_start": 775,
      "char_end": 824
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_033",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我吹了吹头发，听着音乐，心情格外舒畅。",
      "sentence_index": 33,
      "char_start": 824,
      "char_end": 843
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_034",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "与此同时，她也在家忙碌着。",
      "sentence_index": 34,
      "char_start": 843,
      "char_end": 856
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_035",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "她戴上眼镜和帽子，仔细地挑选口红颜色，涂好口红后，又认真地化了妆，吹了头发。",
      "sentence_index": 35,
      "char_start": 856,
      "char_end": 894
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_036",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "她也在听着音乐，准备出门。",
      "sentence_index": 36,
      "char_start": 894,
      "char_end": 907
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_037",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我选好了鞋子和配饰，准备出门。",
      "sentence_index": 37,
      "char_start": 907,
      "char_end": 922
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_038",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "出门前，我给她发了条消息，确认了时间。",
      "sentence_index": 38,
      "char_start": 922,
      "char_end": 941
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_039",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "然后关掉空调和手机，离开了家。",
      "sentence_index": 39,
      "char_start": 941,
      "char_end": 956
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_040",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "刚出门不久，她的电话就打了过来，我有点紧张地接了电话。",
      "sentence_index": 40,
      "char_start": 956,
      "char_end": 983
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_041",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "挂了电话后，我直奔花店，买了12朵漂亮的花。",
      "sentence_index": 41,
      "char_start": 983,
      "char_end": 1007
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_042",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我拿着花，心里想着她，想象着她收到花时开心的样子。",
      "sentence_index": 42,
      "char_start": 1005,
      "char_end": 1032
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_043",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "终于，我见到了她，把花递给了她。",
      "sentence_index": 43,
      "char_start": 1030,
      "char_end": 1048
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_044",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "她开心地接过花，我们相视而笑。",
      "sentence_index": 44,
      "char_start": 1046,
      "char_end": 1063
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_045",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我们一起去了约定的酒吧。",
      "sentence_index": 45,
      "char_start": 1061,
      "char_end": 1075
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_046",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "在酒吧里，她问我要不要回家，但我更想和她在这里多待一会儿。",
      "sentence_index": 46,
      "char_start": 1073,
      "char_end": 1104
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_047",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我们点了啤酒，聊着天。",
      "sentence_index": 47,
      "char_start": 1102,
      "char_end": 1115
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_048",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "突然，我看到一些奇怪的东西，感到有些惊讶。",
      "sentence_index": 48,
      "char_start": 1113,
      "char_end": 1136
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_049",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "不过，和她在一起的时光总是很愉快，虽然中途我去了趟洗手间，但这并不影响我们的好心情。",
      "sentence_index": 49,
      "char_start": 1134,
      "char_end": 1178
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_050",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "凌晨两点，我躺在床上，很快就进入了梦乡。",
      "sentence_index": 50,
      "char_start": 1176,
      "char_end": 1198
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_051",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "在梦里，我看到两个人在激烈地争吵。",
      "sentence_index": 51,
      "char_start": 1196,
      "char_end": 1215
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_052",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "接着，我梦见了2012年世界末日的场景，巨大的海浪淹没了地球，人们纷纷逃到山上避难。",
      "sentence_index": 52,
      "char_start": 1213,
      "char_end": 1259
    }
  ],
