      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "她喜欢香奈儿，可我没那么多钱，根本买不起。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_782",
      "target_id": "sent_004",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "走着走着，我瞧见一家书店，心想送本书当礼物也挺好的。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_783",
      "target_id": "sent_005",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我走进书店，随手翻了几本书，突然想到可以在书里夹一朵玫瑰，可玫瑰花很快就枯萎了，我的心情也跟着支离破碎。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_784",
      "target_id": "sent_006",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我又想到书里说不定藏着坏人，拿枪指着我，心里不免有些害怕。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_785",
      "target_id": "sent_007",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "坏人朝我开枪，我敏捷地躲开了，心里有点来气。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_786",
      "target_id": "sent_008",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我盯着机票看，特别想去旅行，忍不住笑了起来。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_787",
      "target_id": "sent_009",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我幻想着我俩结婚后去度蜜月的场景，不由得笑了。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_788",
      "target_id": "sent_010",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我拿起手机，给她发了条消息。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_789",
      "target_id": "sent_011",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我问她：“结婚以后你想去哪儿度蜜月呀？”",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_790",
      "target_id": "sent_012",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "她回我：“想去自由女神像，还有埃菲尔铁塔……”这时电话响了，我看着机票，心里想着要去悉尼歌剧院、富士山、泰姬陵、加拿大、金字塔……最后定了去美国。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_791",
      "target_id": "sent_013",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "美国那边的景点可多了，有白宫、迪士尼、梦露雕像、体育馆、自由女神像，还有世贸中心。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_792",
      "target_id": "sent_014",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我猛然想起世贸中心被炸过，吃了一惊。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_793",
      "target_id": "sent_015",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我赶紧查了去美国的航班、机场、酒店和旅行攻略。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_794",
      "target_id": "sent_016",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "各种酒店都列出来了，五星级的、三星级的、经济型的都有，还有博物馆、剧院，以及各种各样的奢侈品牌。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_795",
      "target_id": "sent_017",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我顺手点了个赞，笑着继续翻书，走着走着就到了书店门口，正好红灯亮了，我便停了下来。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_796",
      "target_id": "sent_018",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "想到她，我又转身往回走，顺手搜了搜巴黎的景点——巴黎圣母院、蒙娜丽莎、埃菲尔铁塔……不知不觉又走到了书店门口。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_797",
      "target_id": "sent_019",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我刷了卡结账，心里盘算着买两本书当作礼物送给她。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_798",
      "target_id": "sent_020",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "付完钱拿到礼物后，想着她收到一定会特别开心。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_799",
      "target_id": "sent_021",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我盯着手里的礼物，陷入了纠结，不知道该不该送给她。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_800",
      "target_id": "sent_022",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "走出书店后，又想起了她的生日，忍不住回头望了望。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_801",
      "target_id": "sent_023",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我在心里琢磨着：相机太贵了，不买；平板也太贵，不买；滑板还是太贵，不买；游戏不算贵，那就买了吧，想着想着忍不住笑出了声。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_802",
      "target_id": "sent_024",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "想到她和游戏，我还是决定去把账结了。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_803",
      "target_id": "sent_025",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "结完账走出书店，我看了眼时间，就回公司去了。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_804",
      "target_id": "sent_026",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "刷工牌进了大楼，走进电梯时看到快递的牌子，心里有点意外。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_805",
      "target_id": "sent_027",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "按了电梯按钮，电梯一路经过1楼、2楼……最后到了89楼，红灯亮了电梯停下，门一开我就走了出去。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_806",
      "target_id": "sent_028",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "左转、直行、转弯、再直行、转弯、直行，然后打卡、刷手机、开门。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_807",
      "target_id": "sent_029",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "走到自己的工位前，坐了下来。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_808",
      "target_id": "sent_030",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "下午六点，我回到家里，第一件事就是打开空调，让自己凉快凉快。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_809",
      "target_id": "sent_031",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我从冰箱里拿出一瓶饮料，舒舒服服地喝了一大口。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_810",
      "target_id": "sent_032",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "然后我去浴室冲了个澡，出来以后就开始精心挑选晚上约会要穿的衣服，试了好几套，总算是找到了满意的搭配。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_811",
      "target_id": "sent_033",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我吹了吹头发，放着音乐，心情格外舒畅。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_812",
      "target_id": "sent_034",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "与此同时，她也在家里忙着准备。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_813",
      "target_id": "sent_035",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "她戴上眼镜和帽子，仔细地挑了口红的颜色，涂完后又开始认真化妆，还把头发吹干了。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_814",
      "target_id": "sent_036",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "她也一边听着音乐，一边准备出门。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_815",
      "target_id": "sent_037",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我也挑好了鞋子和搭配的饰品，准备出发。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_816",
      "target_id": "sent_038",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "临出门前，我给她发了条信息，又确认了一遍时间。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_817",
      "target_id": "sent_039",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "然后关掉空调和手机，离开了家。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_818",
      "target_id": "sent_040",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "刚出门没一会儿，她的电话就打过来了，我有些紧张地接通了。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_819",
      "target_id": "sent_041",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "挂了电话后，我直奔花店，买了12朵漂亮的花。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_820",
      "target_id": "sent_042",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我手捧着花，心里一直想着她，想象着她收到花时那开心的模样。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_821",
      "target_id": "sent_043",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "终于见到她了，我把花递了过去。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_822",
      "target_id": "sent_044",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "她开心地接过花，我俩相视而笑。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_823",
      "target_id": "sent_045",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我们一起去了约定好的那家酒吧。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_824",
      "target_id": "sent_046",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "在酒吧里，她问我是不是想回家了，可我却更想和她在这儿多待上一会儿。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_825",
      "target_id": "sent_047",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我们点了啤酒，一边喝一边聊。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_826",
      "target_id": "sent_048",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "突然，我看到了一些怪怪的东西，觉得有点惊讶。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_827",
      "target_id": "sent_049",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "不过话说回来，和她在一起的时光总是那么开心，虽然中途我去了一趟卫生间，但这丝毫不影响我们的好心情。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_828",
      "target_id": "sent_050",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "凌晨两点，我躺在床上，不一会儿就进入了梦乡。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_829",
      "target_id": "sent_051",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "梦里，我看见两个人正在激烈地争吵。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_830",
      "target_id": "sent_052",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "接着，我梦到了2012年世界末日的景象，滔天巨浪淹没了整个地球，人们纷纷逃到山上躲避。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
